translation.Name: Kuwait Note #2
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_1: Pretty big day today, caught a bandit tryna bust inta the safe at the
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_2: saloon with nothin' but some good ol' fashioned fisticuffs. Sucker didn't
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_3: even manage two hits before he was out cold and croakin' on the floor!
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_4: Well, by any means, bartender was grateful and gave me a few more drinks on the house.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_5: S'ppose I shouldn'tve drank 'em all in one go though, stepped outside
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_6: and saw this grand ol' metal tube of sorts pop outta nowhere on the horizon!
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_7: The tremendous sound'a somethin' goin' "ZAP!" rollin' through the air like thunder!
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_8: Almost made me buckle to my knees. I'll wait it out in here,
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_9: I reckon there's too much booze in me to think straight.
